{"tid":386638,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「即刻駁咀」名宿反駁奧燒：咁串咀你又唔續約既喂","createTime":"2017-09-04T04:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T16:27:14.000Z","uid":5006,"like":94,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59beeaee0c5a28088c21265127281c6d81d7a8ae","tid":386638,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:46:29.000Z","msg":"前因：<br />\n「大反擊」奧燒貼長文 嗌槍手名宿：收嗲啦！ <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/385272/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/385272/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170904/large/1504495245_d9b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170904%2Flarge%2F1504495245_d9b8.jpg&h=90c9025d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴球星奧斯日前在Facebook貼出長文，對球隊名宿批評他及隊友表現作出擊，並表示希望名宿能停止說話及開始支持他們。不過，之前曾經為奧斯爾辯護的槍手名宿胡禮對奧斯爾是次舉動就不以為然，他形容奧斯爾的貼文「可笑」並質疑這名德國國腳為何仍未與球隊續約。<br />\n<br />\n現年28歲的奧斯爾與阿仙奴合約已到最後一年，胡禮在出席《BBC》電台第五台的節目時就坦言︰「簽約吧，如果你對人們批評球隊反應那麼強烈，那是因為你是阿仙奴成功不可或缺的一員&hellip;&hellip;為甚麼你還未續約？那是我會對你說的，<strong>若你感覺那麼強烈，為何你還未簽約</strong>？」<br />\n<br />\n胡禮又稱︰「<strong>一個在球場上未真正發揮的球員出來叫別人走開</strong>，而他尚未續約，這是可笑的。當他們開始有表現，我們便會停止批評。奧斯爾一直說了很多，但他究竟在做甚麼？簽新約並展示你有多關心阿仙奴。」<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170904&amp;guid=57166728&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170904%26guid%3D57166728%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant&d=kBGhVs4sxn2hb7T1NjVu8LDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=30ba5866\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170904%26guid%3D57166728%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant&h=1bf1f214\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170904&amp;guid=57166728&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：撐奧燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比面你叫你名宿，唔比面你叫你廢老咋，收嗲啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：撐名宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奧燒講一套做一套，拎個盾仔就打晒飛機，約又唔續，抵屌！"},{"pid":"bce175fcf4150c5f0a4e503c00bfa94aa20073ed","tid":386638,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:48:45.000Z","msg":"點解係阿狗特別多25囝"},{"pid":"62ed77301905c6da08cccdc3be74d25fa9bb2027","tid":386638,"uid":54427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:48:58.000Z","msg":"廢佬係到搵存在感，比人屌完都唔收嗲，真係⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ae9b68aa284c853f0f8057826af5cdc79f147f","tid":386638,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:50:20.000Z","msg":"唔續約就唔可以叫你班廢老收聲咩"},{"pid":"60a58ae25b727a5bcc11a6a025df72d090d233a7","tid":386638,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:51:18.000Z","msg":"d名宿咪撚煩啦屌"},{"pid":"227334a851970fbbc8b4b3e6fe6abe098e081f8a","tid":386638,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:52:22.000Z","msg":"有鬥心有heart果d一早轉會啦"},{"pid":"d7e9089ee2c2d4f32014024a72c4d7441d2d4d83","tid":386638,"uid":30040,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"奧燒：人人都踢阿仙奴，唔同人人都踢想阿仙奴咩"},{"pid":"47222d98be8a6caed49e97b1b923c75ca7c4fe07","tid":386638,"uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:53:46.000Z","msg":"胡禮國家隊榮譽<br />\n英格蘭國家隊<br />\nNA<br />\n<br />\n奧燒國家隊榮譽<br />\n世界盃-- 季軍：2010, 冠軍：2014<br />\nU21歐洲國家盃-- 冠軍：2009"},{"pid":"6100360220262a1405